      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a practical choice for someone seeking a reliable daily driver at an accessible price point. The engine and transmission are fully operational and have been consistently maintained to ensure dependable performance. However, please note that the car shows its age with visible exterior scratches and some interior upholstery wear. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle that provides great value for those prioritizing mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection.",
