    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I've taken such good care of this car that it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, babied since day one and kept in pristine shape inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next home. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
