    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive 996.2 wide-body example. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.6L M96.03 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, this unit delivers linear power through a crisp G96/31 six-speed manual gearbox. The viscous-coupling AWD system provides exceptional lateral grip, complemented by a factory-lowered suspension and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and zero evidence of bore scoring or RMS weeping. The chassis rigidity and kinematic integrity remain as-delivered from Stuttgart. A concours-ready specimen for the serious collector.",
